milestones.description: Kyle Coetzer has scored 2 hundreds in ODIs, the most for SCOT breaking Calum MacLeod's record
Dawlat Zadran has broken the record for most ducks (4) in ODIs for AFG, going past Nawroz Mangal's 4

stories.title: Shahzad, bowlers dismantle Scotland
stories.subTitle: Scotland v Afghanistan, 2nd ODI, Edinburgh
stories.seoTitle: Report - Mohammad Shahzad, bowlers help Afghanistan dismantle Scotland
stories.summary: Mohammad Shahzad produced his fifth ODI fifty for Afghanistan, a typically belligerent knock, to set up a 78-run win via the Duckworth-Lewis method over Scotland at The Grange on Wednesday afternoon
stories.byline: The Report by Peter Della Penna in Edinburgh

image.caption: Mohammad Shahzad gave Afghanistan a brisk start
image.longCaption: Mohammad Shahzad gave Afghanistan a brisk start, Scotland v Afghanistan, 2nd ODI, Edinburgh, July 6, 2016
